    "Fuzzy logic systems offer a robust solution for handling uncertainty and providing nuanced decision-making in intrusion detection 57.",
    "Fuzzy logic is based on the concept of \"fuzzy sets, \" which allow gradual transitions between different membership grades.",
    "Unlike traditional binary classifications, where data is either entirely in one category or another, fuzzy logic accommodates the idea data can belong to multiple categories simultaneously.",
    "This is particularly advantageous in intrusion detection, where network behavior may exhibit subtle deviations or uncertainty.",
